<Body>
	<Title>广西境内车辆追尾致6死38伤</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2007-10-8</ReportTime>
	<Content>
    <Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e1" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s1">广西新闻网</Participant><Location lid="l1">南宁</Location><Time tid="t1" type="relTime">10月8日</Time><Denoter did="d1" type="statement">讯</Denoter></Event> (通讯员 胡明军)</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e2"><Time tid="t2" type="relTime">10月8日凌晨3时左右</Time>，一辆广东开往贵州的<Object sid="s2">大客车</Object>在<Location lid="l2">广西境内</Location>发生<Denoter did="d2" type="emergency">追尾</Denoter>事故。</Event></Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e3"><Denoter did="d3" type="emergency">事故</Denoter></Event><Event eid="e4">造成<Object sid="s4">大客车</Object>整体严重<Denoter did="d4" type="stateChange">变形</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e5"><Participant sid="s5">6名乘客</Participant>不幸<Denoter did="d5" type="stateChange">死亡</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e6">另有<Participant sid="s6">38人</Participant><Denoter did="d6" type="stateChange">受伤</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e7">其中<Participant sid="s7">4人</Participant><Denoter did="d7" type="stateChange">受重伤</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e8" type="thoughtevent">据<Denoter did="d8" type="statement">了解</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e9"><Time tid="t9" type="relTime">8日凌晨</Time>，一辆车牌号为贵J02461、由广东开往贵州的<Object sid="s9">大客车</Object>在<Location lid="l9">广西北海至南宁高速公路据大塘收费站10公里处</Location>，与一辆车牌号为桂A29677的<Object oid="o9">大货车</Object><Denoter did="d9" type="action">追尾相撞</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e10">事故造成<Object sid="s10">大客车</Object>整体严重<Denoter did="d10" type="stateChange">变形</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e11"><Location lid="l11">车内</Location><Participant sid="s11">48名乘客</Participant>被<Denoter did="d11" type="stateChange">困</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e12"><Time tid="t12" type="relTime">凌晨3时39分</Time>，<Participant sid="s12,s14">南宁市应急联动指挥中心</Participant><Denoter  type="action" did="d12">接到</Denoter><Object oid="o12"><Event eid="e13"><Denoter did="d13" type="action">报警</Denoter></Event></Object></Event>后立即<Event eid="e14"><Denoter did="d14" type="operation">调集</Denoter><Participant oid="o14" sid="s15,s16">南宁市消防</Participant>、<Participant oid="o14" sid="s15,s16">交警</Participant>、<Participant oid="o14" sid="s15,s16">路政</Participant>、<Participant oid="o14" sid="s15,s16">120</Participant>等部门</Event><Event eid="e15"><Denoter did="d15" type="movement">赶赴</Denoter><Location lid="l15">现场</Location></Event><Event eid="e16"><Denoter did="d16" type="operation">救援</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e17" type="thoughtevent">据南宁市消防部门的<Object sid="s17">消息</Object><Denoter did="d17" type="statement">称</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e18"><Participant sid="s18,s19,s20,s21,s22">救援人员</Participant><Denoter did="d18" type="movement">到达</Denoter>后</Event>，<Event eid="e19">立即<Denoter did="d19" type="action">携带</Denoter><Object oid="o19">破拆工具</Object></Event><Event eid="e20"><Denoter did="d20" type="movement">深入</Denoter>狭小的<Location lid="l20">车内</Location></Event><Event eid="e21">进行<Denoter did="d21" type="action">破拆</Denoter></Event>、<Event eid="e22"><Denoter did="d22" type="action">切割</Denoter></Event>。<Event eid="e23"><Time tid="t23" type="relTime">9时10分</Time>，历经5小时的紧张奋战，<Participant sid="s23">救援人员</Participant>将车内<Participant oid="o23">受伤乘客</Participant>全部<Denoter did="d23" type="operation">救出</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e24"><Participant oid="o24,o25">受伤人员</Participant>已被<Denoter did="d24" type="movement">送往</Denoter><Location lid="l24">广西医科大一附院</Location>、<Location lid="l24">自治区人民医院</Location><Location lid="l24">南宁市江滨医院</Location>等五所医院</Event><Event eid="e25">进行<Denoter did="d25" type="operation">救治</Denoter>。</Event></Sentence></Paragraph>
